The contact capture machine for sales and relationships.

eMiner is a Google Chrome extension that automates the process of searching and capturing leads through search engines to find contacts.

⏱ Speed - Capture thousands of leads per minute through the powers of automation.
🎯 Quantity - Find as many leads as your business needs with minimal effort.
🏆 Quality - Get leads with accuracy of up to 96% of the criteria informed in the searches.

eMiner takes care of designing sophisticated searches through search engines to find, capture, validate and organize the data captured from as many leads as possible across Google Maps, LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, TikTok and over 700 different sources.

WHY EMINER?
✅ Have an infinite supply of hyper-segmented leads forever and multiply your sales conversions;
✅ Use automation superpowers to leverage your business instead of manually mining leads;
✅ Reduce the time and cost of creating and executing ineffective lead capture strategies;
✅ Take full control of the audience and don't be held hostage by the low performance of paid campaigns;

How many opportunities are you leaving behind because you don't have an unlimited source of qualified leads?

